caption:
So I signed up as a writer for @tonystarkbingo​, but most of my writing so far has turned out pretty angsty. Don’t get me wrong, I like the fills I’m done, but I also wanted to do something more light hearted and fun! This video is a project I’ve had in my mind for a while now, combining one of my favorite scores with one of my favorite scenes.

THIS IS NOT THE FINAL VIDEO, hence why I don’t have the proper post structure for the event. THIS IS A PREVIEW so get hyped and I’ll hopefully drop the full video tomorrow (when it’s not 2am and I can get my eyes to focus on premiere’s tiny timeline again)
